name: 3Dplatformer (Swarn "A. Y." S. Warshaneyan)
description:
A three-dimensional (3D) world exploration game created as a part of an coursera course on game design & development by michigan state university (using unity engine's version 2020). 

Modifications made on top of the guided parts: added new levels to play, added instructions, modified GUI to allow access to all levels from the main menu & renamed the game

Created by: Swarn "A. Y." S. Warshaneyan
